[SPEAKER_01] na kojim se područjima želiš dati

270
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:20,099
[SPEAKER_01] ili ti je to još uvijek bilo

271
00:21:20,099 --> 00:21:22,019
[SPEAKER_01] tijekom novicijata i studiranja

272
00:21:22,019 --> 00:21:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] nekako u omaglici

273
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:24,240
[SPEAKER_01] pa si ono rekao

274
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] ok, gospodin će to razjasniti

275
00:21:25,980 --> 00:21:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] kao i sve do sada

276
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] ili si baš imao već tada

277
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] ja želim ići tu,

278
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:31,759
[SPEAKER_01] ja želim ići na tu marginu,

279
00:21:31,819 --> 00:21:33,660
[SPEAKER_01] ja želim povijati rane tima.

280
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:35,799
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je to postalo jasno

281
00:21:35,799 --> 00:21:37,640
[SPEAKER_01] koji su tvoji frontovi?

282
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam uvijek mislio

283
00:21:39,579 --> 00:21:43,160
[SPEAKER_00] evangelizacija, evangelizacija, evangelizacija.

284
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] I to sam mislio

285
00:21:46,059 --> 00:21:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] da će to biti na način pučkih misija

286
