[SPEAKER_00] sve teme i svi uzrasti

294
00:22:01,380 --> 00:22:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] svi slojevi društva i tako dalje.

295
00:22:02,859 --> 00:22:04,240
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam uvijek uvijek

296
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] da bih to želio biti.

297
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] Moj župnik tadašnji

298
00:22:09,019 --> 00:22:10,720
